<h2>What is it?</h2>

<p>
    The future of gaming is Virtual Reality. People will transition from just seeing and playing games on a monitor or TV to almost living in the games.
    With the help of Virtual Technology, one can be fully immersed in any enviroment they desire. Virtual Reality is usually displayed directly to the eyes by wearing a headset.
    The headset completely covers the eyes for an immersive 3D experience. Many prgrams run in VR utilize controllers. They can act as your arms and legs in Virtual space.
    Movement of the controllers register your arms and hands moving while the buttons on the contoler manipualted by your fingers move your person in the space.
    Some headsets let you move around and spin around as much as your power cord and space allow.
</p>

